One of the busiest and well managed metro stations of Hyderabad. Kukatpally Housing Board locality, in general, is a posh residential area, thus the footfall at this station is also high. There are a large number of malls and showrooms around this metro station. The view from the station concourse is absolutely mind-blowing.
